# Keywords – Energy-Efficient Machine Learning Models (Green AI)

| No. | English Keyword | Definition (Short Description) | Persian Translation |
|-----|-----------------|--------------------------------|---------------------|
| 1 | Green AI | Environmentally responsible and energy-efficient artificial intelligence systems. | هوش مصنوعی سبز |
| 2 | Energy Efficiency | Optimization of computational processes to minimize energy consumption. | بهره‌وری انرژی |
| 3 | Machine Learning | Algorithms that enable systems to learn from data automatically. | یادگیری ماشین |
| 4 | Model Compression | Reducing the size and complexity of ML models without losing accuracy. | فشرده‌سازی مدل |
| 5 | Knowledge Distillation | Transferring knowledge from a large model to a smaller, efficient one. | تقطیر دانش |
| 6 | Neural Architecture Search (NAS) | Automated design of optimal neural network architectures. | جست‌وجوی معماری شبکه عصبی |
| 7 | Sustainable Computing | Designing computing systems to be eco-friendly and energy-conscious. | رایانش پایدار |
| 8 | Edge AI | Running AI models on local devices instead of centralized servers. | هوش مصنوعی لبه‌ای |

---

**Source:** *Energy-Efficient Machine Learning Models (Green AI)* — IJPREMS, Vol. 05, Issue 08, August 2025 (Impact Factor: 7.001)
